{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"09d82e6dea","title":"再论无产阶级的革命造反精神万岁","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"6bcef21aeb","index":0,"year":1966,"month":7,"day":4,"articleId":"09d82e6dea"}],"tags":[{"id":"3be4d5766f","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题"},{"id":"3bff1d2fc6","name":"暴力和武斗","type":"主题"},{"id":"4bd6d6f93a","name":"群众运动重要文献","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d48f0ea3e8","name":"造反运动和派别斗争","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","name":"红旗一九六六年第十一期","internal":true,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives2/main/9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3.pdf"},{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"7f8ac6a0df","name":"清华大学附属中学红卫兵"}]},"publication_details":{"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"254544c068","type":"paragraph","text":"再斋无产阶级的革命造反精神万发","index":0,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"a0a5b39858","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义的道理千条万猪，归根结底，就是一句话：造反有理。...根据这个道理，","index":1,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"e31f79c261","type":"paragraph","text":"于是就反抗，就斗季，就干社会主义。","index":2,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"95e90143c8","type":"paragraph","text":"过去，工人打倒资本家，农民打倒地主，剥削阶级速之为造反。无产阶级适反的帽子真是光荣得很！","index":3,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"7dcd12ccad","type":"paragraph","text":"今天，旧思想、旧文化、旧风、旧习惯等等产生修正主义的东西，都完全消灭了吗？","index":4,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"1ddfb293b1","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！","index":5,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"5476b50870","type":"paragraph","text":"各地各单位的黑线黑帮现在都完全消灭了吗？","index":6,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"ce2e3f7431","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！","index":7,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"c0689b8134","type":"paragraph","text":"现在消灭了黑线黑帮，将来就不会产生新的黑线黑帮吗","index":8,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"dd294f1b03","type":"paragraph","text":"不是！","index":9,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"b68ae07aff","type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义，现代修正主义和一切反动派都消灭了吗？","index":10,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"51461f0e3a","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！没有！没有！！！","index":11,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"b0ba29d170","type":"paragraph","text":"在这种情况下，我们无产阶级能不造反吗？无产阶级药革命造反精神怎么能不万岁呢","index":12,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"edb192018f","type":"paragraph","text":"一毛泽东之众，有领导，有武器，有组织，有“野心”，来买不小，切不可等闲视之。","index":13,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"794fcb2495","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的领导是党中央和毛主席！","index":14,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"e70c4130f7","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的武器是战无不胜的伟大的毛泽东思想！","index":15,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"7edb2bb8ce","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的组织是彻底革命的红卫兵！我们的“野心”是横扫一切牛鬼蛇神捷山易，撼红卫兵难！","index":16,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"d4295ead41","type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的右派光生们，我们很理解你们的特殊心情：你们被我们专政了，你们痛苦了，你们也想哦一声“造反”了。无怪乎，最近出现了左派、右派齐赋造反的怪现象。老实告诉你们，珍珠不容鱼日来混杂。我们只许左派造反，不许右派造反！你们胆敢造反，我们就立即镇压！这就是我们的逻辑。反正国家机器在我们手里。","index":17,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"e4ac927904","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级的革命造反精神万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"9557982139","type":"paragraph","text":"清华大学附属中学 红卫兵","index":19,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"dcb14095db","type":"paragraph","text":"1966年7月4日","index":20,"publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea"}],"page":{"id":"1bd8933d99","publicationId":"9ee7a157-a1ac-450b-b7a3-3c22a9c29eb3","articleId":"09d82e6dea","start":30,"end":30}},"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"01e54b6a9f","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"0d9d2be0df","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的武器是战无不胜的伟大的毛泽东思想！","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"197b4a11f3","type":"paragraph","text":"今天，旧思想、旧文化、旧风俗、旧习惯等等产生修正主义的东西，都完全消灭了吗？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"21931565a0","type":"paragraph","text":"现在消灭了黑线黑帮，将来就不会产生新的黑线黑帮吗？","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"3f6b53c4b4","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级的革命造反精神万岁！","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"413e4b06b6","type":"paragraph","text":"各地各单位的黑线黑帮现在都完全消灭了吗？","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"4195f1699d","type":"paragraph","text":"不是！","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"434fb65086","type":"title","text":"再论无产阶级的革命造反精神万岁","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"5b33305609","type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的右派先生们，我们这群造反之众，有领导，有武器，有组织，有“野心”，来头不小，切不可等闲视之。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"6adf16dbd0","type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义，现代修正主义和一切反动派都消灭了吗？","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"6e7c3d837a","type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级的右派先生们，我们很理解你们的特殊心情：你们被我们专政了，你们痛苦了，你们也想喊一声“造反”了。无怪乎，最近出现了左派、右派齐喊造反的怪现象。老实告诉你们，珍珠不容鱼目来混杂。我们只许左派造反，不许右派造反！你们胆敢造反，我们就立即镇压！这就是我们的逻辑。反正国家机器在我们手里。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"7f0d7e81b9","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"89bd6ce704","type":"paragraph","text":"＊                          ＊                      ＊","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"9923463063","type":"paragraph","text":"马克思主义的道理千条万绪，归根结底，就是一句话：“造反有理。”……根据这个道理，于是就反抗，就斗争，就干社会主义。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"bb756c8065","type":"paragraph","text":"过去，工人打倒资本家，农民打倒地主，剥削阶级诬之为造反。无产阶级造反的帽子真是光荣得很！","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"c0bded37a2","type":"paragraph","text":"在这种情况下，我们无产阶级能不造反吗？无产阶级的革命造反精神怎么能不万岁呢？","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"ddc2b459bf","type":"paragraph","text":"没有！没有！！没有！！！","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"de334dd7e3","type":"paragraph","text":"撼山易，撼红卫兵难！","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"de3b8e1779","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的领导是党中央和毛主席！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"e6c0d41f13","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的组织是彻底革命的红卫兵！","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"ea7517a678","type":"paragraph","text":"我们的“野心”是横扫一切牛鬼蛇神！","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"},{"id":"fa9a3bd0c7","type":"paragraph","text":"──毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea"}],"page":{"id":"80d2860011","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"09d82e6dea","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}